text: White Stuff s the eleventh studio album by American band Royal Trux. It was released on March 1, 2019, through Fat Possum Records. It is the band's first album in 19 years. ==Track listing== ==Charts== {| class="wikitable plainrowheaders" |+ Chart performance of White Stuff ! scope="col"| Chart (2019) ! scope="col"| Peak position |- |- |} ==References== Category:2019 albums Category:Royal Trux albums Category:Fat Possum Records albums
